.gitignore for viral-discovery-pipeline

--- General ---

Ignore system-specific files

.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

--- Data Files ---

Ignore large raw and intermediate sequencing data

*.fastq
*.fastq.gz
*.fq
*.fq.gz
*.sra
*.sam
*.bam
*.bai

--- Output Directories ---

Ignore the entire output directories generated by the pipelines

This is the most important rule for this project

.*_analysis/
combined_analysis/

--- Database Files ---

Ignore local copies of large databases

Users should download these themselves
/path/to/db/

--- Python ---

Ignore Python virtual environment folders and cachev

env/
*.pycpy
cache/

--- Conda ---

Ignore conda environment files if you export them locally

conda-env.yml